title: Finca Jorsan stay
text: My experience at Finca Jorsan was absolutely exceptional! Despite a minor hiccup with the entry code, the host's immediate response and availability via phone truly impressed me. Their proactive offer to assist us, even though we didn't ultimately need it, demonstrated their commitment to ensuring guests' comfort and satisfaction. This thoughtful gesture immediately put us at ease and set the tone for a wonderful stay.The cozy atmosphere of the house instantly made us feel right at home, and the jacuzzi was a luxurious touch that added to the overall relaxation. The bedroom offered breathtaking views, while the surrounding landscape was simply awe-inspiring. Our time at Finca Jorsan was truly memorable, and we are hoping to come back soon to experience it all over again.

title: Super friendly and helpful!
text: We had a wonderful experience at Manaeva lodge, that has exceeded our expectations. Reva picked us up in the airport. There is an air conditioned bungalow with rooms that are cozy and inviting. Reva prepared breakfast and dinner for us, both were delicious and extraordinarily convenient. Revâ€™s sister, Heia, took us on a private tour of the island stopping at various points of interest, including secluded waterfalls (the three waterfalls of FA'ARÃšMAT), botanic garden, the Maroa Grotto, Teahupoo, the site of the upcoming surfing competition for 2024 Summer Olympics, a blow hole, and much more.  We circumnavigated Tahiti Nui, and took a gander into Tahiti Iti.  We would definitely return to such warm hospitality provided by this family.
